		Subject:&nbsp;<b>Group Leaders</b></font>
		
		<a href="MB_Editmsg.asp?FID=67&FN=Paladin&SID=7&SN=EverQuest&TID=1453488&TN=Group+Leaders&CAT=Classes&SURL=http%3A%2F%2Fwww%2Eeverlore%2Ecom&MSID=1453488&PL=4&amp;action=REPLY"><img src="http://www.everlore.com/gimages/btn_reply.gif" border="0" align="right" alt="Reply to message"></a>
