		<hr size="1">ADD,</P><P>Group leaders should have a good connection. Having a GL go LD screws you out of time. </P><P>Try to make a GL some one who can gate/port, to invite others. This also lets you use CoH to retrive members from afar.</P><P>As far as what I expect from a GL.</P><P>When I ask a question I want a yes, no or ? RIGHT AWAY.</P><P>If I'm working on something that has a short respawn time, GL not answering quickly can cause more fights or CR if you get back pops.</P><P>Short answers are best.  Long answers explain alot of unneeded detail, especially bad if you have numerous leaders as in Planes, etc.  </P><P>As far as a raid leader.....</P><P>Well, she has to be hot  <img src='http://www.everlore.com/gimages/tongue.gif' width=15 height=15 align=middle></P><P>JK kohi  <img src='http://www.everlore.com/gimages/smile.gif' width=15 height=15 align=middle></P><P></P><P><hr><BR><p align=center> <BR><i><a target=new href=http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=53389>Sularus GloryBringer</a><BR>Knight of Mithaniel Marr & Bringer of his Glory on The Nameless<BR>Leader of <a target=_blank href=http://www.geocities.com/derjohns/Veratae1.html>Veratae's Blade</a><BR>Bane of Evil & Protector of those who walk in the Light</i><BR>Proud Bearer of Soulfire.<BR>Knight of the Silent Watch.</p><BR><p align=center> <a target=new href=http://veratae.cjb.net><img src=http://home.earthlink.net/~derjohns/_uimages/VerataesLogo.jpg border=0></P><p align=center> <br>&nbsp;<br>&nbsp;<br></font>
